Komodo Wallet is a cross-platform cryptocurrency wallet and decentralized exchange (DEX)
that supports multiple blockchain networks. It provides secure storage for various
cryptocurrencies and enables peer-to-peer trading through atomic swaps.

Features:
* Multi-coin wallet supporting various cryptocurrencies
* Decentralized exchange (DEX) functionality
* Atomic swap technology for trustless trading
* Cross-platform support (Web, Desktop, Mobile)
* Secure private key management
* Support for UTXO and ERC-20 tokens
* Hardware wallet integration (Trezor)

The application is built with Flutter and uses the Komodo DeFi SDK for blockchain
interactions. It provides a user-friendly interface for managing digital assets
and participating in decentralized finance.
